title: GMC Buldhana Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 45 Senior Resident Posts
description: Government Medical College (GMC) Buldhana has declared the official notification 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 45 Senior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MD/ MS, and DNB can grab this chance and apply for the GMC Buldhana Recruitment 2025 . Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply before the last date of application....
